Description: Credit & Management Systems is the leading developer of comprehensive system solutions for corporate and commercial credit management.
Full Description: Credit & Management Systems is the leading developer of comprehensive system solutions for corporate and commercial credit management. CMS’s highly acclaimed Corporate Credit Manager ™ (CCM) software system is the most powerful and widely used commercial credit scoring, financial analysis, risk management, and decision support system available. CCM is and has been the accepted generic name for credit management software for over 2 decades. Recognized internationally, CMS is a full service management consulting and software development firm, currently supporting over 1800 users worldwide, including more than 100 global firms having sales in excess of $1 billion. Started in 1985 and incorporated in 1987, CMS’s flagship product was its Corporate Credit Manager system. The CCM system was originally developed as a financial analysis tool in support of the commercial lending group at Citicorp. Through a relationship with the National Association of Credit Management (NACM), the CCM software evolved into a more fully integrated, comprehensive credit management tool kit. CMS was the first and only exhibitor at the NACM conference in Washington, DC in 1985 and has been an active, highly visible attendee at NACM Conferences & Expos every year since. In addition, since 1987, CMS has been a visible, active supporter and participant in Credit Research Foundation (CRF) meetings and several research projects.
